22:17.503 --> 22:20.131
It'll be the best wedding in the country.

22:21.132 --> 22:24.677
I think it's stupid to spend
all that money on a wedding.

22:26.888 --> 22:30.141
I don't think it's stupid,
I find it romantic.

22:30.975 --> 22:32.643
