22:32.894 --> 22:34.437
Don't get upset, honey.

22:34.520 --> 22:37.982
I just don't understand
why people can spend all that money

22:38.024 --> 22:39.067
on a wedding.

22:39.692 --> 22:40.985
Who would do that?

22:42.070 --> 22:44.489
Aurelia Ortiz-Villalobos.

22:46.365 --> 22:48.576
Is she related
to Fernando Ortiz-Villalobos?

22:49.827 --> 22:51.204
She is his daughter.

22:55.208 --> 22:59.337
